to pay it back immediately?

23
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,760
Hello.

24
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,560
What's going on?

25
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,400
Didn't we agree
to acquire Lin Corporation before?

26
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,480
