165
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:57,200
Mrs. Xiao, did you have a quarrel
with Mr. Xiao?

166
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,320
I'll take my leave.

167
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,120
